      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 07 PRICING -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">07, Pricing</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What LG appliance repair costs in Southern California.</h2>

    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $89, applied toward the repair. Labor and parts quoted in writing before any work begins. These ranges reflect typical 2024-2025 LG repair pricing across our service mix.</p>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Diagnostic</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$89</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Waived when you approve repair</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Standard band</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$180–$385</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Door gasket · fan motor · water valve · drain pump · igniter</div>
      </div>
